title: O3b mPower service debut pushed later into 2023
summary: Four of the six O3b mPower broadband satellites that SES had planned to launch this year with SpaceX won’t be ready until early 2023, the operator said Nov. 3 as growth in its networks business boosted total revenues.

title: First O3b mPOWER broadband satellites set for liftoff after quick launch campaign
summary: The first two spacecraft in an 11-satellite refresh of SES’s Medium Earth Orbit O3b internet constellation are poised to rocket into space from Cape Canaveral on Friday, less than two weeks after shipment to the Florida spaceport from a Boeing factory in California already fully fueled and integrated for launch.
